    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那Broker和ActuatorController是作为外部系统节点，还是作为状态？另外，状态之间的触发条件需要标注吗，比如从Still到Moving是由什么触发的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Still",
        "Moving"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Broker和ActuatorController作为外部系统节点，用方框表示。状态流转先画主干：Broker发指令让执行器从Still变成Moving，ActuatorController负责实际驱动。另外Moving可以回到Still，这是正常停止。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主结构画出来：Broker指向Still，Still分出两条线——一条到ActuatorController，另一条到Moving，Moving再连回Still。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker",
        "Still",
        "Moving",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。但还缺一个关键状态：执行器在Moving时可能遇到障碍物或故障，进入Crash状态。Crash之后需要ActuatorController介入复位。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已加上Crash节点：Moving指向Crash，Crash再指向ActuatorController。这样异常处理链路就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Moving",
        "Crash",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "检查一下：Still到ActuatorController这条线是什么意思？应该是ActuatorController驱动状态变化，但Still作为初始状态，是不是应该只有Broker指向它？",
